# Mobile (Flutter 3.24) Conventions

## Tooling
- Flutter 3.24+, Dart 3.5+.
- BLoC (`flutter_bloc`) for ALL state. No Provider, no Riverpod, no GetX.
- Hive for local cache; SQLite via `drift` only if Hive can't represent it.
- GoRouter for navigation.
- Dio for HTTP. Pusher Channels Flutter (Reverb compatible) for WebSocket.
- Firebase Cloud Messaging for push.

